{"tid":1990150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩續神隱專用火車現元山　俄發賀電祝福","createTime":"2020-04-26T13:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T13:00:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7252954e10148880dd4e69a809a249b916c59726","tid":1990150,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0htVditgJhK3lZEAO7Al5ULmNGKBZqfDh6PSZ6ZgZ-dU0gcGgrYnZsF3pAdkp8JWwnMHVhHnwXMEgndGwpMHds/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0htVditgJhK3lZEAO7Al5ULmNGKBZqfDh6PSZ6ZgZ-dU0gcGgrYnZsF3pAdkp8JWwnMHVhHnwXMEgndGwpMHds%2Fw644&h=d4b5f041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hI-Q0QOsEFgJsST7ANwBpVVYfFW1fJQUBCH9HHTMnSDYVKVVQVy8NbE9BQDtCelFcBSxcZUBNDTMSLVFSBS4N/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hI-Q0QOsEFgJsST7ANwBpVVYfFW1fJQUBCH9HHTMnSDYVKVVQVy8NbE9BQDtCelFcBSxcZUBNDTMSLVFSBS4N%2Fw644&h=aae18444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓領袖金正恩自4月11日起一直再無露面，上周二突傳出他接受心血管手術後情況危殆，日媒昨更指他變成植物人，連俄羅斯也突然送上祝福，而衛星圖片則顯示其專列火車停泊在元山。朝中社昨稱，為慶祝金正恩訪俄一周年，俄羅斯聯邦共產黨中央主席久加諾夫上周五向金正恩發賀電，除了指去年4月的會晤加深兩黨友誼及加強兩國合作，久加諾夫還在文末向金正恩「致以祝賀，並祝願你健康幸福」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然外界諸多揣測，但北韓仍對金正恩的健康和身在何處三緘其口，官媒《勞動新聞》今日只稱金正恩對參與三池淵市建設的勞動者致謝，但未提及他本人消息或刊登他的照片。設於美國華盛頓、監察北韓狀況組織「北緯38度」(38 North)昨指衛星拍到金正恩的專列火車，上周二和上周四停泊在東部元山市、金氏家族專用的車站，即使如此也不能證實金正恩在元山，也不能知其健康情況。有南韓官員則說，相信金正恩目前在元山。路透社昨引述消息稱，中國派遣醫療專家在內的小組往北韓，雖不知原因，但令外界更相信金正恩健康出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e6%88%90%e7%96%91%e3%80%91%e9%87%91%e6%ad%a3%e6%81%a9%e7%ba%8c%e7%a5%9e%e9%9a%b1%e5%b0%88%e7%94%a8%e7%81%ab%e8%bb%8a%e7%8f%be%e5%85%83%e5%b1%b1-%e4%bf%84%e7%99%bc%e8%b3%80%e9%9b%bb%e3%80%8c%e7%a5%9d%e7%a6%8f%e3%80%8d-216507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%2581%25a5%25e5%25ba%25b7%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%2596%2591%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%2587%2591%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e6%2581%25a9%25e7%25ba%258c%25e7%25a5%259e%25e9%259a%25b1%25e5%25b0%2588%25e7%2594%25a8%25e7%2581%25ab%25e8%25bb%258a%25e7%258f%25be%25e5%2585%2583%25e5%25b1%25b1-%25e4%25bf%2584%25e7%2599%25bc%25e8%25b3%2580%25e9%259b%25bb%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25a5%259d%25e7%25a6%258f%25e3%2580%258d-216507&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4IVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=9c3516a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e6%88%90%e7%96%91%e3%80%91%e9%87%91%e6%ad%a3%e6%81%a9%e7%ba%8c%e7%a5%9e%e9%9a%b1%e5%b0%88%e7%94%a8%e7%81%ab%e8%bb%8a%e7%8f%be%e5%85%83%e5%b1%b1-%e4%bf%84%e7%99%bc%e8%b3%80%e9%9b%bb%e3%80%8c%e7%a5%9d%e7%a6%8f%e3%80%8d-216507</a>"}]}